Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.95,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.54,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現   夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
