Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.65,0:21:30.88,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.04,0:21:37.72,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.96,0:21:46.35,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:50.65,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.48,0:21:58.99,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:21:59.15,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H96}{\3a&H96}兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.15,0:22:03.33,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.90,0:22:11.46,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.73,0:22:15.97,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.97,0:22:16.01,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&Hdc}{\3a&Hdc}Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.29,0:22:23.52,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.67,0:22:30.48,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.93,0:22:36.03,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.14,0:22:45.04,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.03,0:00:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.45,0:00:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞臺是黑夜中的圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.02,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本之間透露出犯罪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.74,0:00:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次到這裡來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了他帶來的那瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.15,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喝了那個酒身體才復原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果把這個全部喝掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以全部復原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.76,0:01:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼小竟敢喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那些朋友來找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.72,0:01:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我喝了那種酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成高中生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能跟他們幾個在一起的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這就是最後一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.02,0:02:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡放的每一本書都無聊死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這麼無聊的書 叫我怎麼寫心得報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這些書排的還真亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是兒童書報區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出入這裡的都是一些小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.75,0:02:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外國進口的原裝書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.08,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書被反放在書盒裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用保鮮膜包起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些可不是你們小孩子看的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.13,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巡邏車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好發生了什麼案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館長 警察已經到下面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我立刻過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的電梯等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像超重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能坐七個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.87,0:03:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 五 六 七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在七個人 剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了數你自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太是不會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 就走樓梯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生 您就是館長嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓津川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們之所以到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是為了貴圖書館職員玉田和男的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他昨天沒來上班也沒有請假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 出了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他發生了什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.74,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉田先生從前天晚上開始就已經下落不明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽說前天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你在圖書館裡面加夜班吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我那天比玉田先生還要早回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼要到圖書館的倉庫裡去調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定是在回家的途中被什麼人攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉田先生是一個非常認真的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平常在回家之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會從這裡打電話回家先跟太太說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前天晚上他就沒這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說他很有可能是在加班的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什麼人從這裡帶了出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者他現在仍然在圖書館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他非常有可能已經被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.69,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經把這裡所有的地方都查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.34,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是被帶出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.69,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我們先收隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的是太打攪你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.26,0:05:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在所有的人都走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫你們回家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麼辦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去找屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才警方的那些人不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這間圖書館好像有味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}味道和疑問在日文裏音近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有味道啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯在動 有人上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.59,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.50,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館長津川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這個時候來幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個書櫃放的都是那些可疑的進口書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉田那個大傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果不看這個裡面就不會被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些警察也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼容易就收隊回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本就沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉田現在就沉睡在這個圖書館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:06:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來玉田先生的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被他藏在這個圖書館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺他的人就是津川館長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是屍體到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那些書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被反放在書盒裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用保鮮膜包好的原裝書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.16,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在圖書館裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.05,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們還是暫時不要出去比較保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 我肚子好餓 去吃鰻魚飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 他回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從那些箱子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來路不明的原裝書開始查起好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.13,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想裡面的東西一定被他用包包帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還有好多盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有辦法放進包包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放不下的那一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是被館長藏在這個房間的什麼地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之我們現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.18,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在找到那個屍體之前先把那些書找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說現在就輪到我們少年偵探團出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從這個書架開始找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們分成兩隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別調查架子兩邊的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.07,0:09:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.79,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開燈幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.21,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.16,0:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好暗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被館長看到的話 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定已經回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像真的回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有找到什麼奇怪的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 一點也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說應該不是在這個書架上才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們幾乎都把書拿下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太那邊怎麼都沒有把書搬下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把你們那邊的書都給移開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的確已經把書移開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.12,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有封背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排在這裡的每一本書都是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.31,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這些原裝書並不是被反放在書盒裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是書皮外面根本就沒有封背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.94,0:10:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說館長他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在書架的書和書之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又放了這些沒有封背的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書架上總共放了三排的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰把表面的書拿走以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一邊看到的永遠都是書頁的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會以為是對面的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不會發現有這排書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.68,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡又是兒童書報區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡看書的又都是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不會注意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些書之所以放得參差不齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為放書的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.57,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些書被推得太用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就會把對面的書往前推出來一點的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在國外製造這麼奇怪的東西再輸入國內的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想裡面恐怕是手槍或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.96,0:11:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個津川館長其實在進行毒品的走私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他把毒品放在這裡保存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次只要拿一點點出去賣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 玉田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是因為碰巧發現這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.07,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津川館長才會為了秘密不被洩漏出去而殺人滅口的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.89,0:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 怎麼會不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.18,0:11:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故障了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只有出去直接找警察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就直接把屍體給找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我們的功勞就更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到屍體的話 可是大功一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鞋帶又鬆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼暗 怎麼綁得起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.97,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳偏要穿這麼麻煩的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家就喜歡這種鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有人把屍體直接藏在書架上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.97,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較不顯眼的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的時候警方不是都已經派人到處找過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在就沒得找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還有個奇怪的書架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個上面有個奇怪的把手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是移動式書架的把手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動書架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要轉動把手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.48,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.08,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個屍體藏在這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰動了書架都會被立刻發現了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個把手太重了 轉不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快點來幫元太拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二 拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.50,0:13:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面也沒有什麼奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才動不了是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你太重的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你太胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在幾公斤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在四十公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快是我的兩倍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最後一天跟這些小鬼頭混在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要喝下那瓶酒我就會變回高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在才十五公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要減肥了 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.14,0:14:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得上次稱體重的時候是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.12,0:14:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十八公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個電梯等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.93,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.40,0:14:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才到上面的機械室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說屍體就是在那個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是到那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把這個電梯的門切換成手動的模式而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.84,0:15:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們幾個在白天坐電梯的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯因為超重而發出的鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.61,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候是因為我們總共有八個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯的警鈴才會響的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人加起來也不過一百公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大人的一倍半而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再加上當時在電梯裡的四個大人的體重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有身上帶著的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯鈴響的標準也還差一個人的體重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個電梯一開始的時候就有一個人在裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家看不到的電梯的死角…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.01,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.14,0:16:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣子看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他也許是被勒死之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被兇手從上面將屍體丟到電梯的天花板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切的事情都是那個津川館長搞的鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點現在快去報警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.37,0:16:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津…川…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津…津川館長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 到這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟叔叔一起回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.33,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你們幾個人都要照我的話去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個還在討論什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一塊回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要小看我們幾個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館長先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.27,0:16:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經掌握住證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於書架的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.78,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你藏在書裡面毒品的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.91,0:17:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉田先生看到你販毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你殺人滅口的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.10,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵…偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑壘成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群可惡的小鬼頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們逃不掉的 等著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.78,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好趕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.87,0:17:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是剛才下去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要讓電梯停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是袋子裡的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧 小老鼠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一個個殺了你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.92,0:18:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的確是叔叔不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不再生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個快點出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也未免太明顯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書架歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面夾了書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.16,0:18:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的想法畢竟太單純了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓你們孤獨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.28,0:19:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔一定會讓你們四個人一塊到地下作伴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方在我們的聯繫之下 趕到了現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將津川館長抓了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.42,0:19:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也將玉田先生的屍體找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有毒品都被警方扣押了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為江戶川柯南的最後一個案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.03,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也圓滿的落幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才還真是緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這一下一定死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.22,0:19:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的一方永遠會勝利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要對這個身體說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下次再來 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.77,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們四個集合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼困難的案子都會解決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我們下次也要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要對他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.99,0:20:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像要到很遠的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要變成原來的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回高中生工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這瓶酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以變回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你現在才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什麼拖到這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.72,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你的身體可以還原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我只喝了一口而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不相信的話就看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體已經慢慢開始熱起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.75,0:22:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有變回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可能是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.32,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體大概已經對它免疫了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.99,0:23:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免疫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.51,0:23:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.08,0:23:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體雖然因為這個酒的作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.62,0:23:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經還原成高中生一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.61,0:23:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體也對這種酒產生可抵抗的分泌物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.27,0:23:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.45,0:23:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我的量還不夠的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.21,0:23:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.64,0:23:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一口氣喝掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.78,0:23:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.19,0:23:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色好難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.34,0:23:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.42,0:23:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.51,0:23:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是宿醉未醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.13,0:23:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.63,0:23:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經二十六次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.27,0:23:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔哪會打高爾夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.71,0:23:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也說過他拿這些運動器材的運動最沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.77,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.43,0:24:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個"鐺"的一聲到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.43,0:24:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.56,0:24:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是兇手使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手絕對就是那個人不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.29,0:24:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫練習場殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.96,0:24:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.26,0:24:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高爾夫球具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回你們家的爸爸一定要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太的推理也會百發百中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.12,0:24:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還早得很呢
